\n但係非法議會攞返黎嘅不義之財<br />\n一定要貢獻返出黎<br />\n咁佢地所謂「攞政府資源」呢個point先站得住腳"},{"pid":"0b7c738e7220d73f3945fbcdbc433fc9a1669164","tid":2161254,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f510027e979ad3ff7e9ecf3e0656b8e2c70fe82","tid":2161254,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb07adb33ddeb05b5efc7abc3c41c92c91964638","tid":2161254,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"鄺俊宇：有利民生嘅野我地好難反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"正常立法會佢咁講都算 <br />\n如果臨立會呢個非法會議都咁 真係好嘔心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:45:38.000Z","msg":"你仲對泛民有幻想？<br />\n廿幾年啦 醒下啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d188ce369e02ee3806ced1d73021cc25c3f24bea","tid":2161254,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b7c738e7220d73f3945fbcdbc433fc9a1669164","tid":2161254,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f510027e979ad3ff7e9ecf3e0656b8e2c70fe82","tid":2161254,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb07adb33ddeb05b5efc7abc3c41c92c91964638","tid":2161254,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"鄺俊宇：有利民生嘅野我地好難反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"正常立法會佢咁講都算 <br />\n如果臨立會呢個非法會議都咁 真係好嘔心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:45:38.000Z","msg":"你仲對泛民有幻想？<br />\n廿幾年啦 醒下啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"唔係對佢地有幻想 而係要俾壓力佢地應該要咁做"},{"pid":"ea7cd23bdd00d048c9edfbcd397f6cda49efbc84","tid":2161254,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b1ffa8acb9afbd763af8013869c9116b0289fce","tid":2161254,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb053a26b4f10afd942eb981bf3aba2